'''诺贝尔生理学或医学奖'''（{{lang-sv|'''Nobelpriset i fysiologi eller medicin'''}}），通常合稱'''诺贝尔生理医学奖'''或'''諾貝爾生醫獎'''，由[[诺贝尔基金会|诺贝尔基金会]]管理，该奖项每年颁发一次，用于表彰在[[生理学|生理学]]或[[医学|医学]]领域作出重要发现或发明的人。它是五项[[诺贝尔奖|诺贝尔奖]]中的一项，诺贝尔奖是根据[[硝酸甘油炸药|硝酸甘油炸药]]的发明者瑞典化学家[[阿尔弗雷德·诺贝尔|阿尔弗雷德·诺贝尔]]的遗愿于1895年设立的。诺贝尔本人对实验[[生理学|生理学]]很感兴趣，并想为那些通过在实验室的科学发现而取得的新进展设立奖项。诺贝尔奖于每年12月10日的颁奖典礼上授予获奖者，这一天是诺贝尔的逝世纪念日，获奖者将被授予获奖证书及奖金证书。诺贝尔生理学或医学奖奖章的正面与物理学、化学及文学奖奖章相同，都镌刻着诺贝尔的浮雕像；但奖章的背面是独特的。

截至2020年，111次诺贝尔生理学或医学奖被授予了210名男性以及12名女性。第一枚诺贝尔生理学或医学奖于1901年授予[[德国|德国]]生理学家[[埃米尔·阿道夫·冯·贝林|埃米尔·阿道夫·冯·贝林]]，用于表彰他在[[血清|血清]]疗法及[[白喉|白喉]][[疫苗|疫苗]]等方面所做的贡献。[[格蒂·科里|格蒂·科里]]是第一位获得该奖项的女性，她于1947年获得该奖，因其阐释了[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]的[[代谢|代谢]]作用，这对治疗[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]以及解决众多医学问题有重要作用。

== 背景 ==
[[File:AlfredNobel_adjusted.jpg|thumb]]

1833年10月21日，[[阿尔弗雷德·诺贝尔|阿尔弗雷德·诺贝尔]]出生在瑞典[[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]的一个工程师家庭<ref name="Levinovitz5">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 5</ref>。他是一位化学家，同时也是化学工程师和发明家，他在一生中积攒了大量的财富，大部分来源于他的355项发明，其中最有名的便是炸药<ref name="Levinovitz11">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 11</ref>。他对实验生理学很感兴趣，并在法国和意大利设立了自己的实验室进行输血实验。在进行科学研究的同时，他对俄罗斯的[[伊凡·巴甫洛夫|伊凡·巴甫洛夫]]实验室的捐款也很慷慨，并对通过实验室里的科学发现而取得的新进展持乐观态度。<ref name="Feldman237-238">[[#Feldman|Feldman]], pp. 237–238</ref>

1888年，诺贝尔在一家法国报纸上很吃惊地读到了他自己的讣告，标题为“带来死亡的商人死了”。事实上，当时是诺贝尔的弟弟{{Le|路德维希·诺贝尔|Ludvig Nobel|路德维希}}逝世了，而不是诺贝尔。由于对讣告的内容感到不悦并且考虑到遗产可能对他声誉有不好的影响，诺贝尔决定更改他的遗嘱。<ref name="Time">{{cite news | first = Frederic | last = Golden | title = The Worst And The Brightest | date = 2000-10-16 | publisher = Time Warner | url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,998209,00.html | work = [[Time_Magazine|Time Magazine]] | accessdate = 2010-04-09 | archive-date = 2010-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100417050123/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,998209,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>在他最后的遗嘱中，诺贝尔要求将他的财产用于设立一系列奖项，奖励那些在[[物理学|物理]]、[[化学|化学]]、[[和平|和平]]、[[生理学|生理学]]或[[医学|医学]]，以及[[文学|文学]]方面赋予“人类最大利益”的人<ref name="BBCHistory">{{cite web |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/historic_figures/nobel_alfred.shtml |title = History – Historic Figures: Alfred Nobel (1833–1896) |publisher = BBC |accessdate = 2010-01-15 |archive-date = 2013-07-07 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6HwTaPN0s?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/historic_figures/nobel_alfred.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>。诺贝尔在他的一生中写了多次遗嘱，最后一次大约写于距他63岁逝世前的一年多时<ref>{{cite book |last = Sohlman |first = Ragnar |title = The Legacy of Alfred Nobel – The Story Behind the Nobel Prizes |url = https://archive.org/details/legacyofalfredno0000sohl |year = 1983 |publisher = The Nobel Foundation |edition = First |ISBN = 0-370-30990-1 |authorlink = Ragnar Sohlman |page = [https://archive.org/details/legacyofalfredno0000sohl/page/13 13]}}</ref>。由于其遗嘱存在争议，因而一直到1897年4月26日才被[[挪威议会|挪威议会]]批准<ref name="Levinovitz13">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 13</ref>。

诺贝尔死后[[诺贝尔基金会|诺贝尔基金会]]成立以管理其遗产资产<ref name="nobelfoundation">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobelfoundation/index.html |title = The Nobel Foundation |publisher = nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-06-22 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/19960101/http://nobelprize.org/nobelfoundation/index.html |archivedate = 1996-01-01 }}</ref>。1900年，诺贝尔基金会制定的新章程由瑞典国王[[奥斯卡二世|奥斯卡二世]]颁布<ref name="thelocal1">AFP, [http://www.thelocal.se/14776/20091005/ "Alfred Nobel's last will and testament"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thelocal.se/14776/20091005/ |date=20130503135355 }}, ''[[The_Local|The Local]]''(5 October 2009): accessed 20 January 2010.</ref><ref name="Levinovitz14">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 26</ref>。根据诺贝尔的遗嘱，由瑞典的[[卡罗琳学院|卡罗琳学院]]，这一医学院及研究中心来负责生理学或医学奖<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.infoplease.com/spot/nobel-prize-history.html |title = Nobel Prize History — |publisher = Infoplease.com |date = 1999-10-13 |accessdate = 2010-01-15 |archive-date = 2013-07-07 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6HwTcKHl2?url=http://www.infoplease.com/spot/nobel-prize-history.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。<!--<ref name=BritannicaWill>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/416856/Nobel-Prize "Nobel Prize]" (2007), in ''[[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]]''. Retrieved 15 January 2009, from ''Encyclopædia Britannica Online'': {{quote|After Nobel's death, the Nobel Foundation was set up to carry out the provisions of his will and to administer his funds. In his will, he had stipulated that four different institutions—three Swedish and one Norwegian—should award the prizes. From Stockholm, the Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences confers the prizes for physics, chemistry, and economics, the Karolinska Institute confers the prize for physiology or medicine, and the Swedish Academy confers the prize for literature. The Norwegian Nobel Committee based in Oslo confers the prize for peace. The Nobel Foundation is the legal owner and functional administrator of the funds and serves as the joint administrative body of the prize-awarding institutions, but it is not concerned with the prize deliberations or decisions, which rest exclusively with the four institutions. }}</ref>-->现在该奖项通常被称为诺贝尔医学奖<ref name="Levinovitz112">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 112</ref>。

==提名与评选流程==
对于诺贝尔来说把奖项授予一项新发现且该发现带给人类最大利益这两点很重要<ref name="Lindsten">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/articles/lindsten-ringertz-rev/index.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine, 1901–2000 |last = Lindsten |first = Jan |author2 = Nils Ringertz |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-07-11 |archive-date = 2013-05-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530234118/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/articles/lindsten-ringertz-rev/index.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。遗嘱的每项条款，只用于挑选有资格提名该奖项候选人的代表。这包括来自世界各地的学院成员，有来自瑞典，丹麦，挪威，冰岛和芬兰的医学教授，以及在其他国家选定的大学和研究机构的教授。以前的诺贝尔奖获得者也可提名候选人。<ref>{{cite book |last = Foundation Books National Council of Science |first =  |title = Nobel Prize Winners in Pictures |url = http://books.google.com/?id=_K2RaFgFPCUC&printsec=frontcover |year = 2005 |publisher = Foundation Books |ISBN = 81-7596-245-3 |page = viii}}</ref>直到1977年，才开始由卡罗林斯卡学院的所有教授共同决定诺贝尔生理学或医学奖的获奖者。那一年，瑞典法规的改变迫使该学院将与诺奖有关的全部文献都公之于众，这使人们意识到了为诺奖工作建立一个合法的独立机构的必要性。诺贝尔大会由此建立，它由卡罗林斯卡学院的50名教授组成。大会负责选举出由5名评成员组成诺贝尔委员会，以评估候选人，大会还要选出执行秘书，并且每年还要选出10名附属成员来协助对候选人的评估。1968年，新增的一则条款规定每项诺贝尔奖的获奖者不得超过三名。<ref name="Levinovitz17">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 17</ref>

委员会的任务是负责选出那些在基础科学领域做出贡献的研究者，而不是已做出应用贡献的人。[[哈维·库兴|哈维·库兴]]，发现了[[库兴氏综合征|库兴氏综合征]]的美国[[神经外科|神经外科]]先驱人物，从未被授予该奖项，同样境况的还有 [[西格蒙德·弗洛伊德|西格蒙德·弗洛伊德]]，因为其[[精神分析学|精神分析理论]]缺乏可以进行实验测试的假说。<ref name="Feldman238">[[#Feldman|Feldman]], p. 238</ref>公众期待[[乔纳斯·索尔克|乔纳斯·索尔克]]或[[阿尔伯特·沙宾|阿尔伯特·沙宾]]能够获奖，因其推动了[[脊髓灰质炎疫苗|脊髓灰质炎疫苗]]的发展。但最终该奖授予了[[约翰·恩德斯|约翰·恩德斯]]，[[托马斯·韦勒|托马斯·韦勒]]和[[弗雷得里克·罗宾斯|弗雷得里克·罗宾斯]]，他们在实验室的准备工作中发现脊髓灰质炎病毒可以在猴子的细胞中增殖，这一发现是使得脊髓灰质炎疾病得以根除的基础性发现。<ref name="bishop">{{cite book |last = Bishop |first =  J. Michael |title = How to Win the Nobel Prize: An Unexpected Life in Science |url = http://books.google.com/?id=jJqgBtk58akC&printsec=frontcover |year = 2004 |publisher = Harvard University Press |ISBN = 0-674-01625-4|pages=23–24}}</ref>

20世纪30年代，经典[[生理学|生理学]]领域获诺奖比较频繁，但随后该领域开始终结，继而至专业领域。最后的经典生理学领域的获奖者是[[约翰·卡鲁·埃克尔斯|约翰·埃克尔斯]]，[[艾伦·劳埃德·霍奇金|艾伦·霍奇金]]和[[安德鲁·赫胥黎|安德鲁·赫胥黎]]，他们在1963年因发现“在中枢和外周神经系统的整体电活动”而获奖。<ref name="Feldman239">[[#Feldman|Feldman]], p. 239</ref>

== 奖项 ==
每位诺贝尔生理学或医学奖获奖者都会获得一枚[[金质奖章|金质奖章]]，一份{{Le|获奖证书|Diploma}}和一笔奖金<ref>{{cite web |author = Tom Rivers |date = 2009-12-10 |url = http://www1.voanews.com/english/news/europe/2009-Nobel-Laureates-Receive-Their-Honors-78989292.html |title = 2009 Nobel Laureates Receive Their Honors | Europe| English |publisher = .voanews.com |accessdate = 2010-01-15 |archive-date = 2012-12-14 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6CtjwKvsx?url=http://www.voanews.com/content/article-2009-nobel-laureates-receive-their-honors-78989292/368898.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。这些会在诺贝尔宴会厅被授予。

===奖章===
诺贝尔奖的奖章由瑞典的{{le|铸币工场|Myntverket}}<ref>{{cite web | title = Medalj – ett traditionellt hantverk | publisher = Myntverket | url = http://www.myntverket.se/products.asp?lang=sv&page=3 | language = sv | accessdate = 2007-12-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071218102934/http://www.myntverket.se/products.asp?lang=sv&page=3 | archivedate = 2007-12-18 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>（一家私人公司）铸造，该奖章是诺贝尔基金会的注册商标。每枚奖章的正面都镌刻有诺贝尔左侧轮廓的浮雕像。物理学奖，化学奖，生理学或医学奖以及文学奖奖章的正面都相同，都刻有诺贝尔的浮雕像和他的生卒日期（1833–1896）。在1980年之前，奖章是由23k金铸造的；之后的奖章都是由18k绿金，再镀以23k金铸成的。<ref name="ceptualinstitute1">{{cite web |url = http://www.ceptualinstitute.com/galleria/awards/nobel/nobelmedals.html |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071219125630/http://www.ceptualinstitute.com/galleria/awards/nobel/nobelmedals.html |archivedate = 2007-12-19 |title = The Nobel Medals |publisher = Ceptualinstitute.com |accessdate = 2010-01-15 |deadurl = yes }}</ref>

由卡罗林斯卡医学院授予的奖章上的图案是“一位医学天才在她的膝上放着一本打开的书，为了给生病的女孩解渴，正在收集从岩石上涌出的水”。奖章上刻的话取自[[维吉尔|维吉尔]]的史诗《[[埃涅阿斯纪|埃涅阿斯纪]]》：Inventas vitam juvat excoluisse per artes，翻译为“发明使由艺术装饰的生活更美好。”<ref name="nobelmedal">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/medal.html |title = The Nobel Medal for Physiology or Medicine |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-06-16 |archive-date = 2010-06-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619093004/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/medal.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 证书 ===
诺贝尔获奖者会得到由[[瑞典国王|瑞典国王]]亲自颁发的获奖证书。每位获奖者会获得由授奖机构设计的各具特色的证书，对于诺贝尔生理学或医学奖而言，该证书是由卡罗林斯卡医学院的诺贝尔大会负责，并由瑞典著名的艺术家和书法家制造的。证书包含一张照片、获奖者的姓名以及阐明他们获奖原因的引文文字。<ref name="nobelprize5">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/diplomas/ |title = The Nobel Prize Diplomas |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-01-15 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/19960101/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/diplomas/ |archivedate = 1996-01-01 }}</ref>

=== 奖金 ===
奖金的数额会有所波动，取决于当年[[诺贝尔基金会|诺贝尔基金会]]可颁发金额的多少，并以瑞典货币[[克朗|克朗]]授予<ref name="prizemoney">{{cite web|title = Prize Amount And Market Value Of Invested Capital Converted Into 2009 Year's Monetary Value|format = PDF|url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/about/prize_amounts.pdf|publisher = The Nobel Foundation|accessdate = 2010-08-03|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101015004124/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/about/prize_amounts.pdf|archivedate = 2010-10-15}}</ref>。奖金于1901年首次授出，当时的总金额为150,782克朗（在2009年相当于7,872,648克朗）<ref name="prizemoney">{{cite web|title = Prize Amount And Market Value Of Invested Capital Converted Into 2009 Year's Monetary Value|format = PDF|url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/about/prize_amounts.pdf|publisher = The Nobel Foundation|accessdate = 2010-08-03|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101015004124/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/about/prize_amounts.pdf|archivedate = 2010-10-15}}</ref>。到了2009年，奖金总额达到了10,000,000克朗<ref name="prizemoney" />。由于预算的削减，2012年，每项诺贝尔奖奖金为八百万克朗，即110万美元<ref>{{cite web |url = http://articles.cnn.com/2012-06-11/world/world_europe_nobel-prize-cut_1_nobel-prize-nobel-foundation-alfred-nobel?_s=PM:EUROPE |title = Nobel prize amounts to be cut 20% in 2012 |publisher = CNN |date = 2012-06-11 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120709002611/http://articles.cnn.com/2012-06-11/world/world_europe_nobel-prize-cut_1_nobel-prize-nobel-foundation-alfred-nobel?_s=PM:EUROPE |archivedate = 2012-07-09 |access-date = 2015-10-11 }}</ref>。如果某一奖项同时有两名获奖人，则奖金被平分；如果同时有三名获奖人，授奖委员会可以选择将奖金均分三份，或者授予其中一名获奖者一半的奖金，再授予其他两名获奖者各四分之一的奖金<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2009/oct/05/nobel-prize-medicine-2009-award |title = Nobel prize for medicine shared by scientists for work on ageing and cancer |publisher = Guardian |date = 2009-10-05 |accessdate = 2010-01-15 |location = London, England |first = Ian |last = Sample |archive-date = 2009-10-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091008143238/http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2009/oct/05/nobel-prize-medicine-2009-award |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===颁奖典礼及宴会===
该奖在庆典仪式上被授予，随后将进行晚宴<ref name="local">{{cite news |url = http://www.thelocal.se/23784/20091210/ |title = Pomp aplenty as winners gather for Nobel gala |date = 2009-12-10 |publisher = The Local |accessdate = 2010-06-22 |archive-date = 2009-12-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091215055502/http://www.thelocal.se/23784/20091210/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。诺贝尔晚宴很奢侈，其菜单会提前数月开始筹备，并进行保密，直到宴会当天才会揭晓。首先由选定的国际知名大厨呈递菜单，再由诺贝尔基金会进行品尝和测验后，选定出最终的菜单。现在的晚宴有三道菜，而在1901年时原本有六道菜。每位诺贝尔奖得主最多可带16位客人，并且瑞典王室成员也位列其中。通常，总理和其他政府成员以及诺贝尔家族的代表都会出席。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report_nobel-laureates-dinner-banquet-tomorrow-at-stokholm-city-hall_1321860 |title = Nobel Laureates dinner banquet tomorrow at Stokholm City Hall |date = 2009-12-09 |publisher = DNA |accessdate = 2010-06-18 |archive-date = 2012-01-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120121030656/http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report_nobel-laureates-dinner-banquet-tomorrow-at-stokholm-city-hall_1321860 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 获奖者 ==
{{Main list|诺贝尔生理学或医学奖得主列表}}

[[File:Lorenz_and_Tinbergen1.jpg|thumb]]（左），[[康拉德·洛伦兹|康拉德·洛伦兹]]（右）因其在动物行为方面的发现被授予（还有[[卡尔·冯·弗里希|卡尔·冯·弗里希]]）该奖。<ref name="nobel-1973">{{cite web
 |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1973/index.html
 |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1973
 |access-date = 2007-07-28
 |publisher = Nobel Foundation
 |archive-date = 2018-12-26
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226094904/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1973/index.html%0A%20
 |dead-url = no
 }}</ref>
]]

第一枚诺贝尔生理学或医学奖于1901年被授予德国生理学家[[埃米尔·阿道夫·冯·贝林|埃米尔·阿道夫·冯·贝林]]<ref name="Feldman242">[[#Feldman|Feldman]], p. 242.</ref>。他发现的[[抗血清|血清疗法]]在白喉和破伤风疫苗方面的进展，无疑“给了医生一把战胜疾病和死亡的有利武器”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1901/index.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1901 Emil von Behring |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-07-01 |archive-date = 2018-12-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226101908/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1901/index.html%0A%20 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Behring">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/articles/behring/index.html |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080513155541/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/articles/behring/index.html |archive-date = 2008-05-13 |title = Emil von Behring: The Founder of Serum Therapy |website = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-07-01 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。1902年，该奖项被授予了[[罗纳德·罗斯|罗纳德·罗斯]]，因其在疟疾研究方面的工作，“他揭示了疟疾是如何进入机体的，因此为成功地研究这一疾病以及找出战胜该疾病的方法奠定了基础”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1902/index.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1902 Ronald Ross |website = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-20 |archive-date = 2018-12-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226101808/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1902/index.html%0A%20 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。他指出蚊子是疟疾的传播源，并孜孜不倦地致力于研究能阻断疟疾在全世界范围内传播的措施<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/510100/Sir-Ronald-Ross |title = Sir Ronald Ross |publisher = Encyclopædia Britannica |access-date = 2010-06-20 |archive-date = 2010-07-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100715111654/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/510100/Sir-Ronald-Ross |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1902/ross-bio.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1902 Ronald Ross |website = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-21 |archive-date = 2012-04-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120429234011/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1902/ross-bio.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。1903年的获得者是[[尼尔斯·吕贝里·芬森|尼尔斯·吕贝里·芬森]]，他也是第一位丹麦获奖者，“以表彰他在[[光照治疗|用集中的光辐射治疗疾病]]，尤其是{{Le|寻常性狼疮|Lupus vulgaris}}方面的贡献，他也因此开创了一条医学科学研究的新途径”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1903/index.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1903 Niels Ryberg Finsen |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-07-01 |archive-date = 2018-12-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226102358/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1903/index.html%0A%20 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1903/press.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1903 Niels Ryberg Finsen – Award Ceremony Speech |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-07-01 |archive-date = 2010-10-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101016133338/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1903/press.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在获得该奖后不到一年，他就去世了，终年43岁<ref name="finsen">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1903/finsen-bio.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1903 Niels Ryberg Finsen – Biography |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-21 |archive-date = 2017-06-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170602002958/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1903/finsen-bio.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。 [[伊万·巴甫洛夫|伊万·巴甫洛夫]]的工作也得到了诺贝尔协会的赞赏和支持，由于其在[[消化作用|消化]]生理学研究中的工作而获得了1904年的诺贝尔生理学或医学奖<ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1904/index.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1904 Ivan Pavlov |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-16 |archive-date = 2018-12-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226094906/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1904/index.html%0A%20 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

后来对候选人的选择范围更加广阔以确保其覆盖了生理学或医学领域。该奖项于1973年授予了[[尼古拉斯·廷贝亨|尼古拉斯·廷贝亨]]，[[康拉德·洛伦兹|康拉德·洛伦兹]]和[[卡尔·冯·弗里希|卡尔·冯·弗里希]]，以表彰其对动物[[行为科学|行为模式]]的观察，这更像是属于行为科学领域的奖项而不是医学或生理学领域<ref name="Levinovitz112" />。庭伯根在其接受诺贝尔奖时的演说中对“诺贝尔基金会奖将今年的‘生理学或医学奖’授予了至今仍被视为‘纯粹的动物观察家’的三人这一非常规决策”表示了惊讶<ref name="Tinbergen">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1973/tinbergen-lecture.pdf |title = Ethology and Stress Diseases |last = Tinbergen |first = Nikolaas |date = 1973-12-12 |website = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-16 |archive-date = 2009-03-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327093737/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1973/tinbergen-lecture.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

该项诺贝尔奖得主涉及与生理学或医学有关的广阔领域。{{As of|2010}}，8枚奖项授予了在[[G蛋白|G蛋白]]和[[第二信使系统|第二信使]]的[[訊息傳遞_(生物)|信号转导]]这一领域有贡献的专家，13枚授予了在神经生物学领域的贡献，<ref name="nervesignaling">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/nerve_signaling.html |title = Nobel Prizes in Nerve Signaling |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-16 |archive-date = 2010-06-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619102046/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/nerve_signaling.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>还有13枚授予了在中间[[代谢|代谢]]领域的贡献<ref>{{cite web | title = The Nobel Prize Awarders | website = Nobelprize.org | url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/articles/lindsten-ringertz-rev/index.html | access-date = 2008-11-21 | archive-date = 2013-05-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530234118/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/articles/lindsten-ringertz-rev/index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。至2009年，共计100枚诺贝尔生理学或医学奖被授予了总共195人<ref name="factsmedprize">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/shortfacts.html |title = Facts on the Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-19 |archive-date = 2010-07-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100725010741/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/shortfacts.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="prizefacts" />，其中有十二名女性：[[格蒂·科里|格蒂·科里]]（1947），[[罗莎琳·耶洛|罗莎琳·耶洛]]（1977），[[巴巴拉·麦克林托克|巴巴拉·麦克林托克]]（1983），[[丽塔·列维-蒙塔尔奇尼|丽塔·列维-蒙塔尔奇尼]]（1986），[[格特鲁德·B·埃利恩|格特鲁德·埃利恩]]（1988），[[克里斯汀·纽斯林-沃尔哈德|克里斯汀·纽斯林-沃尔哈德]]（1995），[[琳达·巴克|琳达·巴克]]（2004），[[弗朗索瓦丝·巴尔-西诺西|弗朗索瓦丝·巴尔-西诺西]]（2008），[[伊丽莎白·布莱克本|伊丽莎白·布莱克本]]（2009），[[卡罗尔·格雷德|卡罗尔·格雷德]]（2009），[[邁-布里特·莫澤|邁-布里特·莫澤]]（2014），和[[屠呦呦|屠呦呦]]（2015）<ref>{{cite web |title = Women Nobel Laureates |publisher = Nobelprize.org. |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/lists/women.html |accessdate = 2008-11-21 |archive-date = 2013-06-22 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6HYcdcXKS?url=http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/lists/women.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。只有一位女性——[[芭芭拉·麦克林托克|芭芭拉·麦克林托克]]，在该领域单独获得了诺贝尔奖，她发现了[[转座子|转座子]]<ref name="factsmedprize" /><ref name="McClintock">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1983/mcclintock.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1983 Barbara McClintock |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-06-21 |archive-date = 2010-06-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100608225942/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/1983/mcclintock.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[马里奥·卡佩奇|马里奥·卡佩奇，]][[马丁·埃文斯|马丁·埃文斯]]和[[奥利弗·史密斯|奥利弗·史密斯]]获得了2007年的诺贝尔生理学或医学奖，以表彰其发现的[[基因打靶|基因打靶]]（一种[[遺傳重組|基因重组]]类型），他们通过引入小鼠体内的[[同源重組|同源重组]]，使[[基因剔除小鼠|基因剔除小鼠的]]发育自始至终利用[[胚胎干细胞|胚胎干细胞]]<ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2007/inwinnerdex.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 2007 Mario R. Capecchi, Sir Martin J. Evans, Oliver Smithies |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-06-20 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="Hansson">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2007/adv.html |title = The 2007 Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine – Advanced Information |last = Hansson |first = Göran K |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-06-26 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101016091331/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2007/adv.html |archivedate = 2010-10-16 }}</ref>。诺贝尔生理学或医学奖有37次授予了个人，31次同时授予两人，33次同时授予三人（允许授予人数的上限）。

2009年，该项诺贝尔奖授予了美国的[[伊丽莎白·布莱克本|伊丽莎白·布莱克本]]，[[卡罗尔·格雷德|卡罗尔·格雷德]]和[[杰克·绍斯塔克|杰克·绍斯塔克]]，因其发现了[[端粒|端粒]]（[[染色体|染色体]]末端的[[DNA|DNA]]重复序列的区域）和[[端粒酶|端粒酶]]保护[[染色体|染色体]]的机理。他们共享了 10,000,000[[瑞典克朗|克朗]]的奖金（略高于100万欧元，或140万美元）<ref name="Wade">{{cite news |url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/06/science/06nobel.html |title = 3 Americans Share Nobel for Medicine |last = Wade |first = Nicholas |date = 2009-10-05 |newspaper = The New York Times |publisher = nytimes.com |access-date = 2010-06-22 |archive-date = 2010-06-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619055249/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/06/science/06nobel.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。意大利[[神经学|神经学]]家[[丽塔·列维-蒙塔尔奇尼|丽塔·列维-蒙塔尔奇尼]]与同事[[斯坦利·科恩|斯坦利·科恩]]共同获得了1986年的诺贝尔生理学或医学奖，因其发现了{{Le|神经生长因子|Nerve growth factor}}，丽塔·列维-蒙塔尔奇尼是第一个达到100岁的诺贝尔奖得主<ref name="prizefacts">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/nobelprize_facts.html |title = Nobel Prize Facts |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-15 |archive-date = 2007-02-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070202025710/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/nobelprize_facts.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[File:Gerty_Theresa_Cori.jpg|upright]]在1947年成为第一个获得诺贝尔生理学或医学奖的女性。
]]

=== 时间因素和死亡 ===
因为一些发现或发明的意义可能经过很长时间才显现出来，一些奖是在发现或发明出现若干年后才被授予的。芭芭拉·麦克林托克在1944年的发现，直到1983年才获得诺奖，而他的发现早于DNA分子结构的发现。相似的，[[裴顿·劳斯|裴顿·劳斯]]在1916年发现了鸡体内肿瘤病毒的作用，但直到50年后的1966年才获得诺奖。<ref name="Levinovitz114">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 114</ref><!--The 2008 award was shared by  [[Harald_zur_Hausen|Harald zur Hausen]], who discovered the connection  between the [[human_papillomavirus|human papillomavirus]] and [[cervical_cancer|cervical cancer]], and [[Françoise_Barré-Sinoussi|Françoise Barré-Sinoussi]] and [[Luc_Montagnier|Luc Montagnier]] who jointly discovered  [[HIV|the human immunodeficiency virus (HIV)]].<ref name="harmon" />-->诺奖得主[[卡罗尔·格雷德|卡罗尔·格雷德]]也是在其研究发表20多年后才获奖。她指出时间的沉淀对医学科学来说是一项有益条件，因为一项发明或发现的意义可能经过很长时间才能显现。<ref name="Dreifus">{{cite news |url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/13/science/13conv.html?_r=1&ref=nobel_prizes |title = On Winning a Nobel Prize in Science |last = Dreifus |first = Claudia |author-link = Cladia Dreifus |date = 2009-10-12 |newspaper = The New York Times |via = nytimes.com |access-date = 2010-06-22 |archive-date = 2012-01-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120113163315/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/13/science/13conv.html?_r=1&ref=nobel_prizes |dead-url = no }}</ref>在诺奖历史上，2009年医学领域第一次出现了同年不止一名女性获得诺贝尔奖的情况<ref name="harmon">{{cite web |url = http://www.scientificamerican.com/article.cfm?id=nobel-prize-medicine-2009-genetics |title = Work on Telomeres Wins Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine for 3 U.S. Genetic Researchers (Update) |last = Harmon |first = Katherine |date = 2009-10-05 |publisher = Scientific American |access-date = 2010-06-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091211165529/http://www.scientificamerican.com/article.cfm?id=nobel-prize-medicine-2009-genetics |archive-date = 2009-12-11 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。也是首次同时有两名女性获得诺贝尔生理学或医学奖<ref name="discoverynews">{{cite web |url = http://news.discovery.com/human/nobel-prize-medicine.html |title = Cancer researchers win the Nobel Prize in medicine |date = 2009-10-05 |publisher = Discovery News |accessdate = 2010-06-22 |archive-date = 2010-08-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100812221706/http://news.discovery.com/human/nobel-prize-medicine.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2011年，加拿大免疫学家[[拉尔夫·斯坦曼|拉尔夫·斯坦曼]]获得了诺贝尔生理学或医学奖；但诺贝尔委员会并不知道，在公告发出的三天前，他已经去世了。之后，委员会决定遵循诚信原则，仍将该奖项授予他。

=== 争议人选及排除 ===
{{Main|诺贝尔奖争议}}

一些奖项仍存有争议。针对谁有资格因发现胰岛素是控制糖尿病的中心激素而获得1923年的诺贝尔生理学或医学奖（于该发现发表的一年后被颁发）<ref name="Judson291">{{cite book |last = Judson |first = Horace |title = The great betrayal: fraud in science |url = http://books.google.com/?id=Dhz_u1hgDmoC&printsec=frontcover |year = 2004 |publisher = Houghton Mifflin Harcourt |ISBN = 0-15-100877-9 |page = 291 }}</ref>，引发了热烈的讨论。该奖授予了[[弗雷德里克·班廷|弗雷德里克·班廷]]和[[约翰·麦克劳德|约翰·麦克劳德]]；这一结果却激怒了班廷，他认为麦克劳德的参与是最少的。麦克劳德是[[多伦多大学|多伦多大学]]的部门主任，并未直接参与研究。班廷认为他的实验室搭档[[查理斯·贝斯特|查理斯·贝斯特]]共同承担了该发现的实验室工作，应该和他共享该奖。为公平起见，他决定将他所获奖金的一半分给贝斯特。麦克劳德则认为后来加入实验室队伍的生物化学家{{Le|詹姆斯·科利普|James Collip}}也应获得该奖，并将他的奖金与詹姆斯·科利普分享。<ref name="Judson291"/>还有一些人主张[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]布加勒斯特医药大学的生理学教授{{Le|尼可莱·包勒斯克|Nicolae Paulescu}}是第一个分离出胰岛素的人，在1916年，尽管他提取的泛激素是一种不纯的水提物，并不适合人类治疗，类似于生物化学家克莱尔先前使用过的<ref name="J. Nutrition 92">{{cite journal |url = http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/reprint/92/4/507.pdf |author = The American Institute of Nutrition |title = Proceedings of the Thirty-first Annual Meeting of the American Institute of Nutrition |journal = Journal of Nutrition |volume = 92 |year = 1967 |page = 509 |format = PDF |access-date = 2015-10-11 |archive-date = 2020-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200710113225/https://jn/article-abstract/92/4/507/4778409?redirectedFrom=fulltext |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="nrjs">{{Cite journal |last = Paulesco |first =  N.C. |journal = Archives Internationales de Physiologie |title = Recherche sur le rôle du pancréas dans l'assimilation nutritive. |volume = 17 |issue = |pages = 85–103 |date = 1921-08-31 }}</ref><ref name="nrps">{{cite journal |last = Lestradet |first = H. |journal = Diabetes & Metabolism |title = Le 75e anniversaire de la découverte de l'insuline |volume = 23 |issue = 1 |page = 112 |year = 1997 |url = http://www.em-consulte.com/en/article/79613 |access-date = 2015-10-11 |archive-date = 2015-10-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151011134251/http://www.em-consulte.com/en/article/79613 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在支持他得诺奖的文件中<ref name="nrks">{{Cite journal |last = Banting FG, Best CH. |first =  |journal = Journal of Laboratory and Clinical Medicine |title = The internal secretion of pancreas |volume = 7 |issue =  |pages = 251–266 |year = 1922 |publisher =  |url = http://www.biology.buffalo.edu/courses/bio130/medler/banting.pdf |dead-url = yes |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100623223114/http://www.biology.buffalo.edu/courses/bio130/medler/banting.pdf |archive-date = 2010-06-23 |access-date = 2015-10-11 }}</ref>，包勒斯克已经为他的发现注册了专利（1922年4月10号，专利号6254 (8322) ，"泛激素及其制造过程"，出处为罗马尼亚工业与贸易部）<ref name="nrms">{{cite journal |last =  Murray |first =  Ian |journal = Journal of the History of Medicine and Allied Sciences |title = Paulesco and the Isolation of Insulin |url =  https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-the-history-of-medicine-and-allied-sciences_1971-04_26_2/page/150 |volume= 26 |issue= 2 |pages= 150–157 |year = 1971 |pmid = 4930788 |doi = 10.1093/jhmas/XXVI.2.150 }}</ref><ref name="nrns">{{cite journal |last = Murray |first = Ian |journal = Scottish Medical Journal |title = The search for insulin |volume = 14 |issue = 8 |pages = 286–293 |year = 1969 |pmid= 4897848 }}</ref><ref name="nrqs">{{cite journal |last =  Pavel |first = I. |title = The Priority of N.C. Paulescu in the Discovery of Insulin |publisher = Academy of the Socialist Republic of Romania |year = 1976 |url = |trans_title = Prioritatea lui N.C. Paulescu în descoperirea insulinei }}</ref>。

1926年，頒發給丹麥科學家[[約翰尼斯·菲比格|約翰尼斯·菲比格]]，以表彰其發現引發老鼠癌症的研究。不過後來發現菲比格主張的「寄生蟲引發老鼠癌症」的研究，其實是飲食缺乏[[維生素A|維生素A]]而引發；同時諾貝爾委員會卻忽略以焦油成功誘發兔子耳朵上產生腫瘤的日本科學家[[山極勝三郎|山極勝三郎]]，諾貝爾委員會也拒絕撤回頒發給菲比格的成就。

[[File:Montagnier-Barré-Sinoussi-zur_Hausen-press_conference_Dec_06th,_2008-1.jpg|thumb]]发现[[人乳头状瘤病毒|人乳头状瘤病毒]]以及[[弗朗索瓦丝·巴尔-西诺西|弗朗索瓦丝·巴尔-西诺西]]和[[吕克·蒙塔尼耶|吕克·蒙塔尼耶]]因发现[[艾滋病病毒|艾滋病病毒]]而获得该奖后引发丑闻与争议。]]

1949年，不顾医学机构的抗议，葡萄牙神经学家[[安东尼奥·埃加斯·莫尼斯|安东尼奥·埃加斯·莫尼斯]]获得了诺贝尔生理学或医学奖，因其发明的前额脑白质切除术的发展。他在术后10天后宣布了手术的成功，并由此提出[[前脑叶白质切除术|前脑叶白质切除术]]。由于获奖而导致的大量宣传，导致该手术在未考虑现代[[醫學倫理學|医学伦理]]的情况下就被使用。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》等刊物都曾有过关于该手术的有利报导。据估计，在该手术的人气衰退前，在美国已进行过约40,000例的前额脑白质切除术<ref>{{cite book |title = The Lobotomist: A Maverick Medical Genius and His Tragic Quest to Rid the World of Mental Illness  |url = https://archive.org/details/lobotomistmaveri0000elha  |last = El-Hai  |first = Jack |year = 2005 |publisher = Wiley |ISBN = 0-471-23292-0 |page = [https://archive.org/details/lobotomistmaveri0000elha/page/14 14]}}</ref>。[[约瑟夫·肯尼迪|约瑟夫·肯尼迪]]——即[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]的父亲，让女儿{{Le|露丝玛丽·肯尼迪|Rosemary Kennedy|露丝玛丽}}进行了这一手术，结果致使她只能在社会福利机构度过余生<ref name="Feldman287">[[#Feldman|Feldman]], p. 287</ref><ref>{{cite news |last = Day |first = Elizabeth |url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2008/jan/13/neuroscience.medicalscience |title = He was bad, so they put an ice pick in his brain... |newspaper = The Guardian |publisher = Guardian Media Group |access-date = 2010-03-31 |date = 2008-01-12 |archive-date = 2010-01-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100118102821/http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2008/jan/13/neuroscience.medicalscience |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

1952年的诺贝尔生理学或医学奖，被单独授予了[[赛尔曼·瓦克斯曼|赛尔曼·瓦克斯曼]]，因其发现了链霉素，但忽略了他的共同发现者[[艾伯特·沙茨|艾伯特·沙茨]]<ref name="pharmj">{{cite journal |last = Ainsworth |first = Steve |title = Streptomycin: arrogance and anger |journal = The Pharmaceutical Journal |volume = 276 |year = 2006 |pages = 237–238 |url = http://www.pharmj.com/pdf/articles/pj_20060225_streptomycin.pdf |accessdate = 2010-06-22 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070621142735/http://www.pharmj.com/pdf/articles/pj_20060225_streptomycin.pdf |archivedate = 2007-06-21 }}</ref><ref name="Wainwright">Wainwright, Milton ''"A Response to William Kingston, "Streptomycin, Schatz versus Waksman, and the balance of Credit for Discovery""'', Journal of the History of Medicine and Allied Sciences – Volume 60, Number 2, April 2005, pp. 218–220, Oxford University Press.</ref>。沙茨就这一发现的细节和功劳对瓦克斯曼提起诉讼；最终沙茨赢得了诉讼，并和瓦克斯曼同时成为被官方认可的链霉素的共同发现者，并拥有相关的专利权。但是，他并未被授予诺奖。<ref name="pharmj" />

1962年的诺贝尔奖授予了[[詹姆斯·杜威·沃森|詹姆斯·杜威·沃森]]，[[弗朗西斯·克里克|弗朗西斯·克里克]]和[[莫里斯·威尔金斯|莫里斯·威尔金斯]]，以表彰其在[[DNA|DNA]]的结构与性质方面所做的工作，但未承认其他人的贡献，如[[艾力克·斯托克斯|艾力克·斯托克斯]]和[[贺伯特·威尔森|贺伯特·威尔森]]。另外，[[埃尔文·查戈夫|埃尔文·查戈夫]]，[[奥斯瓦尔德·埃弗里|奥斯瓦尔德·埃弗里]]和[[罗莎琳·富兰克林|罗莎琳·富兰克林]]（其关键DNA的X射线晶体学工作是最详细的，但在三人中获得的承认却最少<ref name="franklin">{{cite web |url = http://profiles.nlm.nih.gov/KR/Views/Exhibit/narrative/dna.html |title = The Rosalind Franklin Papers |last = U.S. National Library of Medicine |work = The DNA Riddle: King's College, London, 1951–1953 |website = USA.gov |access-date = 2010-06-19 |archive-date = 2010-06-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100618060720/http://profiles.nlm.nih.gov/KR/Views/Exhibit/narrative/dna.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{page needed |date = March 2015}}）对沃森和克里克解决DNA分子的结构问题有着直接的贡献，但埃弗里在1955年去世，富兰克林于1958年逝世，而[[诺贝尔奖|诺贝尔奖]]不允许提名逝者。然而公布的诺贝尔奖提名的文件显示，即便富兰克林当时还在世，也无人提名她。<ref name="Fredholm">{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/educational/medicine/dna_double_helix/readmore.html |title = The Discovery of the Molecular Structure of DNA – The Double Helix |last = Fredholm |first = Lotta |date = 2003-09-30 |publisher = Nobelprize.org |access-date = 2010-06-16 |archive-date = 2010-06-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619185453/http://nobelprize.org/educational/medicine/dna_double_helix/readmore.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>威尔金斯唯一的贡献就是把罗莎琳·富兰克林关键的X射线照片展示给了沃森<ref name="nytimesnobel" />。沃森对富兰克林及她在双螺旋发现中的作用的歪曲，体现在他存有争议的《[[双螺旋：发现DNA结构的故事|双螺旋]]》一书中，这也导致了富兰克林在科学界成为典型的性别歧视受害者<ref name="Holt">{{cite web |url = http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2002/10/28/021028crbo_books |title = Photo Finish: Rosalind Franklin and the great DNA race. |last = Holt |first = Jim |date = 2002-10-28 |publisher = The New Yorker |accessdate = 2010-06-19 |archive-date = 2010-11-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101103024725/http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2002/10/28/021028crbo_books |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title = The double helix and the 'wronged heroine' |author = Brenda Maddox |journal = Nature |volume = 421 |pages = 407–408 |date = 2003-01-23 |url = http://www.biomath.nyu.edu/index/course/hw_articles/nature4.pdf |pmid = 12540909 |doi = 10.1038/nature01399 |format = PDF |issue = 6921 |access-date = 2015-10-11 |archive-date = 2016-10-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161017011403/http://www.biomath.nyu.edu/index/course/hw_articles/nature4.pdf |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。查戈夫则不甘心被诺贝尔奖排除在外，他痛苦地写信给其他科学家，表达他对分子生物学领域的失望<ref name="nytimesnobel">{{cite news |title = No Nobel Prize for Whining |author = Judson, Horace |date = 2003-10-20 |url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&res=9C02E4DE123EF933A15753C1A9659C8B63 |publisher = ''New York Times'' |accessdate = 2010-06-23 |archive-date = 2009-08-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090816081427/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2008年的诺贝尔奖授予了[[哈拉尔德·楚尔·豪森|哈拉尔德·楚尔·豪森]]，肯定了他关于[[人類乳頭瘤病毒|人类乳头瘤病毒]]（HPV）可引起[[子宮頸癌|宫颈癌]]这一发现，同时[[弗朗索瓦丝·巴尔-西诺西|弗朗索瓦丝·巴尔-西诺西]]和[[吕克·蒙塔尼耶|吕克·蒙塔尼耶]]也因发现[[艾滋病毒|艾滋病毒]]（HIV）而获得了该奖<ref>{{cite web |url = http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2008/index.html |title = The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 2008 Harald zur Hausen, Françoise Barré-Sinoussi, Luc Montagnier |publisher = Nobelprize.org |accessdate = 2010-06-20 |archive-date = 2008-10-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081009040944/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2008/index.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[罗伯特·加洛|罗伯特·加洛]]或吕克·蒙塔尼耶是否在发现艾滋病致病病毒中贡献更多，这一问题一直饱受争议<ref name="science nobel">{{cite journal |author = Cohen J, Enserink M |title = Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine. HIV, HPV researchers honored, but one scientist is left out |journal = Science |volume = 322 |issue = 5899 |pages = 174–5 |date = October 2008 |pmid = 18845715 |doi = 10.1126/science.322.5899.174 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last = Enserink |first = Martin |author2 = Jon  Cohen |date = 2008-10-06 |title = Nobel Prize Surprise |journal = Science Now |publisher = AAAS |url = http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2008/10/06-01.html |dead-url = yes |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101212065201/http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2008/10/06-01.html |archive-date = 2010-12-12 |access-date = 2015-10-11 }}</ref>。结果是加洛被排除在外，未能获诺贝尔奖。另外当时有一宗丑闻，哈拉尔德·楚尔·豪森正在被调查，原因是由HPV引起的宫颈癌的疫苗所带来的经济利益。阿斯利康公司在两个利益丰厚的HPV疫苗中拥有股份，并且可以从该奖中获得经济利益，该公司已经同意赞助诺贝尔媒体和诺贝尔网站。据泰晤士在线报道，两名选择了楚尔·豪森的参与筛选流程的资深人员，也与[[阿斯利康|阿斯利康]]公司联系紧密。<ref name="AstraZeneca">{{cite news |url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/europe/article5367941.ece |title = AstraZeneca row as corruption claims engulf Nobel prize |last = Charter |first = David |date = 2008-12-19 |newspaper = The Sunday Times |publisher = timesonline.co.uk |access-date = 2010-06-22 |dead-url = yes |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5qpa5pF7G?url= http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/europe/article5367941.ece |archive-date = 2010-06-28 }}</ref>

2018年的诺贝尔奖授予了[[本庶佑|本庶佑]]和[[詹姆斯·艾利森|詹姆斯·艾利森]]，以表彰他们在癌症免疫疗法领域的贡献，但首先發現PD-L1的[[陈列平|陈列平]]與其他2位主要科學家（相關5人同獲{{le|Warren Alpert基金会奖|Warren Alpert Foundation Prize}}）没有获奖<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.pharmacodia.com/web/newinfo/information_8a2d9837612b05a101614f13d0840e1e.html|title=陈列平可能会获诺贝尔奖的的几个理由|access-date=2018-10-01|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001220522/https://news.pharmacodia.com/web/newinfo/information_8a2d9837612b05a101614f13d0840e1e.html|archive-date=2018-10-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://tech.sina.com.cn/d/f/2018-10-01/doc-ifxeuwws0187907.shtml|title=陈列平与诺奖失之交臂，但他的贡献远比诺奖重要|access-date=2018-10-01|author=知识分子|date=2018-10-01|publisher=|archive-date=2018-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001145017/https://tech.sina.com.cn/d/f/2018-10-01/doc-ifxeuwws0187907.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

因为诺贝尔奖的规则不允许提名亡者，长寿也成为获奖的资本，甚至有一项研究在长达50年之后才获得此奖。同时诺贝尔奖也禁止同一奖项的获奖者超过3人，鉴于过去半个世纪以来科学家们越来越倾向于团队合作，这一制度也导致了一些争议。

=== 获奖者数量的限制 ===
1968年颁布的条款规定：任何诺贝尔奖项的获得者都不得超过三人，这引起了广泛的争议<ref name="Levinovitz17" /><ref name="Levinovitz61">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 61</ref>。自20世纪50年代以来，诺贝尔生理学或医学奖的得主多于一人已呈上升趋势。在上世纪前50年共有59人获得该奖，而1951至2000年期间，共有113人获奖。这种增加可归因于二战后国际科学界的崛起，导致更多的人对于某个研究发现都有贡献，并得到特定奖项的提名。同时，当前的生物医学研究更多的是以团队进行而不是由个别科学家单独进行，使得不太可能是任何一个科学家，甚至一些科学家，是某一研究发现的主要贡献者；<ref name="bishop" />这也就意味着当一个奖项的提名可能有超过三名参与者时会被自动排除在外<ref name="Levinovitz114" />。同时由于每一奖项的获得者不得超过三人这一限制，应得的贡献者可能并未得到提名，从而导致了把一些人排除在提名之外而引发的争议<ref name="Lindsten" />。

== 未授奖年份 ==
期间共有九个年份没有颁发诺贝尔生理学或医学奖（1915–1918，1921，1925，1940–1942），大部分在[[一战|一战]]（1914–1918）或[[二战|二战]]（1939–1945）期间<ref name="prizefacts"/>。1939年，[[阿道夫·希特勒|阿道夫·希特勒]]的[[纳粹德国|第三帝国]]禁止[[格哈德·多马克|格哈德·多马克]]接受该奖<ref name="Levinovitz23">[[#Levinovitz|Levinovitz]], p. 23</ref>。后来格哈德·多马克虽接受了获奖证书和奖章，但并未接受奖金<ref name="prizefacts"/>。

